Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gold General
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. You finally look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. Actually, Big Brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to split Kiriyama's head in half.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dang it, kiddo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was wondering what you were going to say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such a troublesome thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:22.06,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blinding Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prompted by him, I looked at the board...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and quickly came back to my senses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't continue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how bad this is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first thing I felt was shock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I was assailed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...by a wave of embarrassment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until just a minute ago,\Nwhat did I think he was?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Matches against people like that\Nare usually drawn-out battles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not my favorite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell?\N"People like that"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't get irritated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's where he'll eat me alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I be so arrogant?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't get irritated"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I misread his level so much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just wanted to win, so I drew the game out,\Nwaiting for him to make a mistake,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while I thought of him as a player\Nfor nothing more than his "ranking".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can not lose here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't even accurately gauge the strength\Nof the player in front of me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I let my head get filled\Nwith a personal grudge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a Rank A player\Nand I treat him like a side character?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I an idiot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I want to run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to disappear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pitch black...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yet blinding...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I can't breathe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}With that brief clearing of his throat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I understood he was telling me\Nto "calm down".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At his prompting...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...with my mind in a state of confusion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I desperately searched for my next move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I searched...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then I realized...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact that I'd been\Nlooking down my nose at him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact that I just figured out\Nhow wrong I was, and that I'm flustered...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He saw through it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He saw through all of it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and yet, he still sits there quietly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I run away in the middle of the game\Njust because I'm mortified,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it would be truly selfish\Nand he knows that, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I scraped up every last bit\Nof desperation and continued playing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the match ended\Nbefore I could recover at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the post-match review began.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F-From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we replay a bit from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}5-h-Rook! From there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He set it up right away,\Nso that must have been the turning point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F-From here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From a position like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was already going badly for me by then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, if I went to 5-d-Pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same, Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same, Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same, Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2-d-Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same, Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then if I'd done this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1-e-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same, Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about 3-e-Silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same, Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same, Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3-g-Pawn+.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1-e-Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same, Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3-d-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4-b-Silver...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then what about 1-e-Pawn,\Nsame, Pawn, 6-e-Pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5-g-Bishop+, same, Silver, 3-g-Bishop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A complete defeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both the match and my approach...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so embarrassed, my voice trembled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Everything in front of me\Nflickered in black and white.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My insight, everything...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...completely lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smith. Oh, today you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, just here to practice a bit.\NIssa and I were discussing your match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel bad for Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With his inexperience,\Nhe misjudged his opponent's level,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,got blown away, and now feels like\Nhe's lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it. The rashness of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Before this match, that punk only made copies\Nof Mr. Gotou's and your game records.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And I bet he focused on how Gotou\Nhas 20 games, but I only have five.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.83,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Carving
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, I'm right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that kid pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've done something similar\Nbefore in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although it wasn't anything as obvious as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. Well, everyone has.\NWell, a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to remember mine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got Mr. Gotou next, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your best.\NHe's scary, though. His face...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I want to win.\NThough he is scary... His face, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to win, and then play against Souya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Title Match...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving. You want to stop somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I've kind of got something...\N- What, girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not exactly that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine then. Go on. Shoo, shoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll see you. Good game today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:34.86,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harunobu Nikaidou
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.11,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call\NDialing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Kiddo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I won. Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You already watched it online, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he's an interesting fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A jumble of stubbornness and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I cracked\Nhis head open, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I kind of understand\Nwhat you were talking about, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yeah. You think we should invite him\Nto join the workshop?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at Smith's apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I kept you waiting!\NTime for num-nums!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kissy-kissy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a cutie-pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.02,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blinding Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:54.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a Little Water
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'm awake, I couldn't stop thinking\Nabout everything,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I slept.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I kept on sleeping.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that time, I assumed\NI'd be up against Gotou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So instead of getting any regular sleep,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I spent all my time obsessively\Ngoing over the game records,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and neglected to eat and drink for days,\Nso now I crashed and slept like a log.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But at last, it became impossible\Nto keep sleeping.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was dehydrated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The symptoms would go away\Nif I could rehydrate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}...but everything I drank\Ncame right back out the same way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I panicked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad. What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I lose any more water...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:15:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had a faint memory\Nof slowly, slowly lapping up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a sports drink with a pinch of salt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It took me over half a day\Nto summon the energy just to get up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:15.79,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fried Chicken Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The next day, I basically crawled\Nto the neighborhood convenience store.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm an idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm even terrible at depression.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Free - Please take
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Retail, office work...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Programmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hall staff... security...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Driver... kitchen staff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are so many different kinds of jobs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But almost all of them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No experience necessary!\NHigh school graduates (18 and older)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I graduate high school in two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until then, the only way a student\Nlike me can earn money to pay rent{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is to continue playing shogi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have so many matches that my days absent\Nin school is at a risky count...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have to at least graduate high school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I can eventually be able to\Nchoose my own path.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I thought, and so I came to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pass it! Pass it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Number team, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Here we go!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of a sudden, P.E.?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And basketball?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-Where should I be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now, I'll just run so I don't stand out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you over there! Who was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the glasses! Over to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ball came to me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um... Uh, what am I supposed to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The goal is over there,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I should pass it to someone, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, glasses, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good question.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}No good. I don't taste anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It's like chewing on sand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Does this really amount\Nto "not running away"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted memories of not running away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do if I was just\Npretending not to run away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?\NI feel like I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something's different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not the high school student\NI imagined to be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I thought I would be able to handle it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought if I could leave home,\Npay rent, and feed myself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would become an adult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I became an adult,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I wouldn't have to cry anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You're crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NAnd what's this, a job magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A high school student sitting alone on the stairs,\Ncrying while reading a job magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something already crazy\Nabout this whole setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, he's the fifth middle school student\Nprofessional shogi player in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rising star of the shogi world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where to dig in first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}First, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Never mind, just eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who eats cold food when they're depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It might kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reach for something warm instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise you'll lose half your hit points!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:20:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try moving back\Nto your mentor's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have rank-deciding competitions\Nand tournaments throughout the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you go to school, with tests and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,meals to make, laundry, and whatever else\Nis going on around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much for a 17-year-old to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- But...\N- You've exceeded your capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was too bad\Nregarding the Lion King Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it online.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada 8th-Dan. Damn, he's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He came up with Master Souya,\Nbut never stood out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he steadily and persistently\Nmade his way to Rank A.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's the personification of "hard work".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And recently he's been a regular\Nat all the Title Matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You know a lot about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We're the same age, so of course I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada 8th-Dan is also passionate\Nabout popularizing shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a workshop,\Nwhere he helps train young players...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nhow about something like that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Joining a workshop?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should join.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shimada 8th-Dan's workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, Nikaidou 4th-Dan is a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- But...\N- Why not? It would be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to learn from the person\Nwho beat you is a huge opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you've been saying!\NBut-but-but!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If 100 buts opened a door, that'd be fine,\Nbut obviously there ain't no door like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more damn buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Brother. Why can't we\Njust reach out to Kiriyama directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you saying the other day that\Nwe should invite him to join the workshop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to explain, but you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is wait for him\Nto make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a Little Water
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.18,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 15
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama. Look at this.\NIt's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.60,0:24:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.52,0:24:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it. I've never seen\NMr. Shimada like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.44,0:24:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I can still keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really something so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.07,0:24:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry will be just as cute in the next\Nepisode of "March Comes in Like a Lion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.53,0:24:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.66,0:24:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'll be in the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.03,0:24:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? But she's so cute! Why not?!
